AGI - "I proudly play the role played by the government to help unblock the negotiation for the start of the accession path of Ukraine in the European Union and to foster". The President of the Council, Giorgia Meloni, said this to the Senate during his communications to the European Council.
&nbsp;
"We reaffirm our condemnation of the conduct of farce elections in Ukrainian territory."
&nbsp;
"In these days there has been a lot of discussion of the proposal made in particular by France about a possible direct intervention of troops of nations of the European Union in Ukraine. I take this opportunity to reiterate in this Chamber that our position is in no way favourable to this hypothesis, which we consider as a forum for a dangerous escalation, to avoid, instead, at any cost. I hope that this Parliament will be compact in responding with us," he added.
&nbsp;
<h2> The responsibilities of Hamas</h2>
"We can't forget who unleashed the conflict in the Middle East: it was Hamas. The reticence that more and more often meets in rebating it betrays a latent but rampant anti-Semitism that must worry us all". The President of the Council, Giorgia Meloni, said this to the Senate during his communications to the European Council.
&nbsp;
<h2> The sacrifice of Navalny</h2>
"The sacrifice of Navalny in the name of freedom will not be forgotten." The President of the Council, Giorgia Meloni, said this to the Senate during his communications to the European Council.
The cost of freedom
"Freedom has a cost, sovereignty has a cost. Do not believe who tells you that everything can be granted for free. The result often, as you have seen, is that you pay much more". The President of the Council, Giorgia Meloni, said this to the Senate during his communications to the European Council.&nbsp;

